-You spoke up and we heard you! We’ve added back in the ability to see which of your friends are currently online in the Friends list.
-We’ve made some tweaks to the Dashboard so that the tiles don’t shuffle around on you anymore. Now they just stay put, so it’s easier to find what you’re looking for!
-We've restored the Report button on Feed posts in profile cards
-We also went ahead and fixed a few crashes while we were at it.
